OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBangladesh: Women-only     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbeach scrapped after social
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fmedia outcry               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Authorities in Bangladesh have reversed
OL,6, their decision to open a women-only    
OL,7, beach after facing accusations they    
OL,8, were pandering to hardline Islamists.  
OL,10,FOn Thursday officials had opened a 150m
OL,11,F(492ft) section of Cox's Bazar for     
OL,12,Fwomen and children, but hours later    
OL,13,Fannounced they were scrapping the idea.
OL,15,FThe decision to segregate the beach was
OL,16,Fmade following requests from some      
OL,17,Fwomen, officials had said.             
OL,19,FBangladesh is a Muslim-majority country
OL,20,Fand remains largely conservative.      
